-- Bharti Airtel Names Two New Executives to Strengthen Its African Operation
-- B y   J o h n s t o n e   O l e   T u r a n a
-- 2010-11-02T06:36:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/bharti-airtel-names-two-new-executives-to-strengthen-african-operation.html
Bharti Airtel Ltd. appointed Tay Kim
Lee as director of internal assurance and Eben Albertyn as chief
technical officer to strengthen its Africa operations, the New
Delhi-based company said in an e-mailed statement today.  Lee joined from Singapore International Group and Albertyn
from MTN Cameroon, Bharti Airtel Chief Executive Officer for
Africa, Manoj Kohli, said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  